comments: Hart (LAL) has his arm extended during his shot and makes marginal contact with Booker (PHX).
Johnson (PHX) is in Kuzma's (LAL) path before the contact occurs.
Ayton (PHX) places his arm to Ingram (LAL) during the pick, but does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Hart (LAL) makes incidental contact with Booker (PHX) after releases the ball and does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Oubre Jr. (PHX) makes clean contact to the ball during James' (LAL) drive towards the rim.
Ingram (LAL) is established in a back screen position behind Bridges (PHX) when Ayton (PHX) runs into Bridges.
James (LAL) makes marginal contact to the body of Johnson (PHX), but does not affect his ability to defend the driving shot attempt by James.
Booker (PHX) pushes off Ingram (LAL) to clear space and receive the hand off.
Ayton (PHX) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
LATR shows James (LAL) extends into Oubre Jr. (PHX) and dislodges him from his legally obtained position.
Hart (LAL) extends his leg in a wide position in Ayton's (PHX) path during his drive, impeding his progress toward the rim.
Ayton (PHX) makes contact to the body of James (LAL) during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Ingram (LAL) makes clean contact to the loose ball during the rebound.
Ayton (PHX) is established in Ingram's (LAL) path before the contact occurs.
Kuzma (LAL) dislodges Johnson (PHX) from his legal guarding position.
Ingram (LAL) has an arm to Bridges (PHX) on his drive when he stops and releases.
Kuzma (LAL) commits a take foul on Johnson (PHX).
